  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-759deb62-4743-42a6-9c7e-0a702e74786b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-da91fa21-2b90-4c10-b804-27c0b6548bf1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-31601c19-2646-4630-a6ed-28c78e304bcd\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 47</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c1f8f2ac-0605-4f92-85f5-7d30d17d8e1f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c50ba73-0f8e-4821-b93b-b8e03fecf2df\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-643c26cf-3af5-49fe-a346-9e4f7f95d3a9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-abd7306b-7567-4fce-bf5d-35b97f9fade5\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 관리자페이지 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-30841607-6d0b-461f-ad2a-52f6ad4f5ed8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-72b0e546-bdcc-4c6a-b5dd-548ab8ade9af\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 관리자페이지 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 관리자페이지의 기획 및 스토리보딩 작업에 집중해 보겠습니다. 이제 2023년 다시 시작입니다. 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-622aa79f-77a9-4d61-be0f-002264e0e79f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b39e310c-e18c-463d-96a1-06e76a2790d4\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e25778ec-1777-46c7-addf-617fc6b79d40\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4beca96f-be32-43b5-ad57-ebb60cc71d34\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0854d1f4-dd73-4dea-bc3e-c4145d6e2146\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9408a15c-bc1c-4c01-aef6-5f5b5d5aae2c\" style=\"color:#444444;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>관리자페이지의 시작</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line4\" id=\"SE-78d69b88-5850-470e-9280-26f29de20e79\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line4 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e00352c2-0efd-46e4-9cf9-3c5ba66a321f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e936e902-05f8-4724-92b1-c2b2b54e1847\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9ff954a6-f17d-488d-b83a-b6df97abe258\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 관리자 페이지까지 겸한 스토리보딩을 연재하겠습니다. vba를 통한 엑셀프로그램을 11회까지 연재했습니다. 1차로 완성은 했고 2차 개발을 준비중에 있습니다. 이 엑셀에서 관리해야 할 부분을 (주)파파스컴퍼니 관리자페이지에 녹이겠습니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4eeff267-72b0-4c64-82f9-21ab69b26c8f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0d36974b-60d8-4cee-a1af-1c65515f4661\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2bdf96bd-1ea4-4dbc-bc94-d054b92b850c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f5a95759-582b-488b-9c2f-c55ebfdfd993\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b></b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8fec2dfb-e71a-480d-9e2e-92a716ff91cf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4764e7f6-d4e9-4b26-ac35-05eaacb3720e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d2451663-0149-4ecb-8b7d-12395b7f5799\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-table_layout1\" id=\"SE-e1863edd-d735-439c-9982-444755c6b5c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-table_layout1 se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 42%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px 0px 0px 1px;border-color:#00b3f2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 255.0px; border-style:solid;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#00b3f2; background-color: #f7f7f7;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e19c688-fa31-499e-acc2-31a1b9fe5cad\" style=\"line-height